lead_paragraph: Steady chants of: "Keep coach O" streamed out of LSU's locker room after the 25th-ranked Tigers got a 54-39 win over No. 22 Texas A&M on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Guice Runs for LSU-Record 285 Yards, No. 25 Tigers Roll
